00:07:29.190 --> 00:07:29.520
Okay.

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:31.510
But...

00:07:32.950 --> 00:07:34.080
Young Master Fugui,

00:07:34.270 --> 00:07:35.600
Chief Hongye

