should already be inside by now.

00:07:38.270 --> 00:07:39.560
If he finds out...

00:07:41.870 --> 00:07:42.630
If he finds out

00:07:42.630 --> 00:07:44.090
you can't see right now...

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:45.740
As long as I don't lose,

